snippet.title: No Man's Sky PlayStation VR2 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Announcing...No Man's Sky for PlayStation VR2.

The power of PlayStation 5, coupled with the all-new PlayStation VR2 hardware, including the new Sense controllers, combine together to take the sense of immersion and believability up another level.
